Package teachersV2

This package contains all classes for manipulation.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Evaluation Contains all the evaluation for the corrected student, the grader (professor) and the mark.
Professor The professor can put marks to students depending of the promotion, the id of the student and if he wants to add/modify a mark.
Promotion The Promotion permits to sort students in promotions to know where they belong to.
Student A student is represented with an id, a promotion if he got one and can have marks (10 the maximum).
